Class GenerateInspectionsMojo

java.lang.Object
org.apache.maven.plugin.AbstractMojo

All Implemented Interfaces:
org.apache.maven.plugin.ContextEnabled, org.apache.maven.plugin.Mojo
@Mojo(name="generate-inspections") public class GenerateInspectionsMojo extends AbstractAtlasMapMojo
The Generate Inspections Mojo performs offline inspection and writes down the inspection result Document into a JSON file.
